OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy morning with rain
OL,6,Fspreading eastwards and giving some
OL,7,Fheavy downpours at times, especially
OL,8,Fover Shetland. Cloud and rain clearing
OL,9,Fto the east in the afternoon with long
OL,10,Fsunny spells developing. Fresh to
OL,11,Fstrong southwesterly winds becoming
OL,12,Fnorthwesterly.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FA dry evening with patchy
OL,15,Fcloud and late sunny spells. Staying
OL,16,Fmostly dry with clear spells
OL,17,Fovernight, but an isolated light
OL,18,Fshower possible. Fresh northwesterly
OL,19,Fwinds becoming westerly.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
