OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FA largely dry day with sunny
OL,6,Fspells and the odd isolated shower
OL,7,Fpossible. Cloud spreading northwards
OL,8,Finto Orkney in the afternoon. Light
OL,9,Fwesterly winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,12,FRemaining unsettled with scattered
OL,13,Fshowers or longer spells of rain at
OL,14,Ftimes spreading eastwards,
OL,15,Finterspersed with drier and brighter
OL,16,Fspells. Often windy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
